Package com.skobbler.ngx

Contains classes needed for initializing the SKMaps framework.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SKMapsDownloadListener
    Listener for download operations.
    SKPrepareMapTextureListener
    Listener for events related to preparing map resources needed in order to inialize the library.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Config
    Contains the properties for the build
    SKCategories
    Keeps all supported main categories and categories.
    SKCoordinate
    Stores information about a coordinate.
    SKMaps
    SKMaps provides support for general settings and management that concerns the whole SKMaps SDK.
    SKMapsInitSettings
    Class that stores settings information for initializing the library.
    SKMercatorCoordinate  
    SKPrepareMapTextureThread
    Handles preparing of map data textures.
    SKProxySettings
    Class used for the proxy used by the framework for internet requests.
    SKStorageManager
    Handles multiple storage methods.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SKCategories.SKPOICategory
    Specifies types of categories for an SKSearchResult.
    SKCategories.SKPOIMainCategory
    Specifies the main categories.
    SKMaps.SKDistanceUnitType
    Distance unit type enum.
    SKMaps.SKLanguage
    Stores possible values for languages supported by the SDK.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SKDeveloperKeyException
    Thrown to indicate that the application needs a developer key in order to use it.
    SKMapsInitializationException
    Thrown to indicate that the application has attempted to use the SKMaps library without initializing it.
    SKMapsPathsNotInitializedException
    Thrown to indicate that the application has attempted to initialize SKMaps library, calling SKMaps#initializeSKMaps(android.content.Context, SKMapsInitSettings, String) without setting the paths before.
